---
import Header from "@components/header.astro";
import "@styles/global.module.css";
import Scripts from "@components/scripts.astro";
import Footer from "@components/footer.astro";
import Meta from "@components/meta.astro";
import Cursor from "@components/cursor.astro";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <Meta name="VelkySMP Monitor" description="VelkySMP Monitor" />
        <Scripts />
        <Cursor />
    </head>

    <body>
        <Header />
        <main>
            <h1>VelkySMP Monitor</h1>
            <section>
                <h2>Dive into the Heart of VelkySMP</h2>
                <p>
                    VelkySMP Monitor offers a window into the bustling world of
                    our Minecraft server, VelkySMP.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>Unveiling the Server Part</h2>
                <p>
                    At its core lies a nimble Python script, tirelessly
                    gathering data from the server. This data undergoes a
                    transformative journey through both local and remote
                    databases.
                </p>

                <h3>Local Database:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Catalogs current online players alongside their login
                        and logout activities.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Empowers the Python script to compute playtime with
                        precision.
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Remote Database:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Chronicles a comprehensive log of server activities.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Captures individual playtime metrics and personalized
                        player customizations.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>Embark on a Journey with the Website</h2>
                <p>
                    Our website serves as the gateway to this dynamic universe,
                    offering a panoramic view of server activities.
                </p>

                <h3>Unraveling the Interface:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Effortlessly browse through the roster of players on our
                        homepage.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Seamlessly group players based on various criteria like
                        online status, playtime, or even their name's initial.
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Tailored Experience:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Customize your profile with pride flags, country
                        insignias, and more.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Personalize your display name, add a star beside your
                        username, and showcase your last played time.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <p>
                VelkySMP Monitor isn't just a tool; it's a portal to community
                engagement and immersive gameplay experiences. Join us as we
                embark on this thrilling adventure together! ðŸŒŸðŸŽ®
            </p>

            <p>
                <a href="https://velkysmp-mon.vercel.app/">
                    <button>Download</button>
                </a>
                <a href="https://discord.gg/velky">
                    <button>Velky's Discord server</button>
                </a>
            </p>
        </main>
        <Footer />
    </body>
</html>
